happened in this game.} 13. Bd2 $1 Rc2 14. Qb3 Qc7 15. Bd3 Bxd3 16. Qxd3 Rc8 {
It seems as though Black is doing extremely well with his control of the 'c'
file, until you see White's next move...} 17. Ke2 $1 $16 {With the idea of
Rhc1; Black is well developed and has a clear advantage (Van Beek-Iordachescu).
}) 13. Be2 Ne4 14. O-O Nc3 $44 {Black has superb activity in this position.})
10... Rc8 $1 {This move should come naturally to you now!} 11. Qb2 Qb6 (11...
