18. Qxa1 Ba6 19. Bxa6 Qxa6 {With a strong knight against a bad bishop and a
more active queen, Black is on his way to gaining an advantage.} 20. Qb2 Rc8
21. g3 h6 22. Kg2 Qd3 23. h4 {White resigned in this position. But after Ng3,
he would be lost anyway.} 0-1

