Qxa8 36. Qf2 Ra1 37. Qf6 Rxf1+ 38. Kxf1 Bd3+ 39. Kf2 Qg8 40. g4 Be4 41. Ke2 Bc2
42. Kd2 Be4 43. h4 Qf8 44. Ke2 gxh4 45. Qxh4+ Qh6 46. Qe7 Qa6+ 47. Kf2 Kg6 48.
Kg3 Qf1 49. Qd6+ f6 50. Qe6 Qf3+ 51. Kh4 Qh1+ 52. Kg3 Qf3+ {What we saw here
